App|publisher=[[ASCII_Media_Works|ASCII Media Works]]|language=ja|title=存档副本|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160420065127/http://dengekionline.com/elem/000/001/239/1239863/|archive-date=2016-04-20|dead-url=}}</ref>。

